{"word":"ἐπιβαίνω","slug":"ἐπιβαίνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπιβαίνω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, βαίνω</el> ‘go’]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘move so as to be on <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>’, <b>get on<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> mount (an animal) <b><a href='B:470 21:5'>Mt 21:5</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> board (a ship)<b> <a href='B:510 21:1'>Ac 21:1</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>, 2; <a href='B:510 27:2'>27:2</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘move so as to arrive at or be in an area’, <b>set foot in <a href='B:510 20:18'>Ac 20:18</a>; <a href='B:510 21:4'>21:4</a>; <a href='B:510 25:1'>25:1</a></b> (some would place this in 1a)<b>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπιβάλλω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}